('chk-specialization-review', 'ph-specialization', 90, 'checkpoint', 'gate', NULL, NULL, 'Specialization Review Gate', 'Review checkpoint for Specialization Tracks. The learner consolidates evidence from Tabular ML Specialist Track, Computer Vision Specialist Track, NLP Specialist Track, MLOps Specialist Track, identifies unresolved prerequisite gaps, and decides whether to continue, review selected topics, or complete extra practice before the next roadmap segment.', 'This checkpoint acts as a transition gate for the machine learning engineering roadmap. It supports reflection and planning; it is not a certification, mastery test, or claim of job readiness.', 'checkpoint', 'ph-specialization', 15, 90, 3, 'advanced', 95, NULL, NULL, '{"source": "roadmap.sh/machine-learning", "checkpointType": "review", "checkpointPurpose": "phase_review", "reviewMode": "gate", "evidenceRequired": true, "claimLimit": "orientation_and_progress_review_only_not_certification"}'::jsonb, true, true, '["Summarize the main concepts and decisions from Specialization Tracks in practical machine learning engineering terms.", "Identify prerequisite gaps, unclear topics, or risks that should be reviewed before moving forward.", "Create a short evidence artifact that links completed roadmap items to what was learned."]'::jsonb, '["List the roadmap items reviewed for this checkpoint.", "Provide one evidence artifact such as notes, a diagram, a lab result, code, queries, screenshots, or a project review.", "Record at least two gaps, risks, or follow-up actions, or explicitly state that no critical gaps were found.", "Use the result to choose one next step: continue, review selected topics, or complete extra practice."]'::jsonb),
